Jimmy and Jey Uso's reunion is immediately cut short by Bron and Bronson.

The Brons will not let the Usos out here peacefully while Paul Heyman lays in a hospital. Bronson Reed has to hold Bron Breakker back just thinking about it.

Jimmy and Jey Uso are cracking jokes before they reveal the Usos vs Bron Breakker and Bronson Reed at Wrestlepalooza.

LA Knight runs out and attacks the Brons but Knight and Uso aren't friends as they continue to argue.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/546247c4-6d97-4f80-adb4-19e3f56c40d1/15904.jpg?format=original)

