*   ## **_Raquel Rodriguez def. Lyra Valkyria after some interference from Roxanne Perez_**
    

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/18906af5-be92-4473-9ce7-b56382e5f8ef/processed_15920.jpg?format=original)

## **_''My name is AJ Lee and I am your favorite wrestler's wrestler''_**

AJ Lee has returned to Monday Night RAW with the Intercontinental Championship around her waist.

AJ Lee opened up about her mental health journey and how she had to take care of herself before she came back to WWE

She even got a loud “THERAPY!” chant going.

AJ Lee talks about how she ended her career satisfied thinking she had done it all. In her time away she went on a mental health journey, got therapy. She wasn't ok but she's better now.

She was ok watching CM Punk fighting people like Drew McIntyre but she was not ok watching Becky Lynch put her hands on her husband.

Becky Lynch comes out. She wants her championship back. She wants to know what kind of man hides behind their wife, anyway?? She calls out her husband, Seth Rollins.

Rollins comes out and asks for the title back. AJ agrees to give it back if they agree to a tag match at Wrestlepalooza. Rollins says she doesn't call the shots. He's the World Champion. He's going to get in the ring and take the title now.

AJ doesn't let him. CM PUNK appears and tries to take Rollins out with a GTS but he escapes.

Rollins agrees to the match so Punk throws the championship at them.

*   ## **_CM Punk and AJ Lee vs Seth Rollins and Becky Lynch is officially on for Wrestlepalooza!_**
    

