Jey Uso heel turn?!!???!!!!! What!!??

*   ## **_Bronson Reed def. LA Knight_** after interference from Bron Breakker.
    

Earlier in the night Jimmy Uso asked if he and Jey should help LA Knight. Jey said they need to worry about making Bron and Bronson acknowledge them and that LA Knight cost him the World Championship. Jimmy said Jey is starting to sound like Roman. Jey left the building.

Later on LA Knight told Jimmy he doesn't need his help at all and still remembers that Jimmy screwed him out of the WWE CHAMPIONSHIP against Roman Reigns.

As LA Knight gets beat down post match, Jimmy runs out for the save. Jimmy gets speared. Jey returns and saves Jimmy but he gets taken down.

LA Knight actually saves both Usos from a beatdown AND THEN JEY SPEARS LA KNIGHT.

What is going on???!